name: Lieutenant s'Too Vees
Lore: 'Dock mechanic. Installs starfighters cannons. Gambler. Followed Lando from Cloud City. Turned down assignment in rear guard to work on General Calrissian''s starship.',
Text: 'When in battle at a site with Lando or Marmor, adds one destiny to total power only. When he is at a docking bay, once during each of your deploy phases, you may deploy one starship weapon from Reserve Deck on your starfighter present; reshuffle.',
